<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Password Reset Request</title>
  </head>

  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center">
    <div>
      <h2 style="font-weight: bold">Hello, {{username}}</h2>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p style="margin: 0; padding: 0;">
        We received a request to reset your password for the Blackfort Dev Team Ticketing System.
        To set a new password, click the button below.
      </p>
    </div>


    <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <button
        style="background-color: #fc3838; border: none; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer;"
      >
        <a style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase" 
           href="{{data.resetPasswordUrl}}"
        >
          Reset Your Password
        </a>
      </button>
    </div>
    
    <div style="padding: 1rem;">
      <p style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666;">
        This link is only valid for a short time for your security.
      </p>
      <small style="padding: 1rem; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; color: #dc3545;">
        If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</small>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <p>If you have any concerns, feel free to reach out to us:</p>
      <p style="margin: 0; padding: 0;"><small>inquiries@expensetracker.com</small></p>
      <p style="margin: 0; padding: 0;"><small>+63 123 4567 8901</small></p>
      <p style="margin: 0; padding: 0;"><small>#1 Salcedo Village. 123 Makati, City, Philippines, 20189</small></p>
    </footer>

    <div style="padding: 1rem">
      <small>*** This is a system-generated message.
        <span style="font-weight: bolder">DO NOT REPLY TO THIS EMAIL.</span>
        ***</small>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p>
        &copy; 2025 Blackfort Team Ticketing System. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>